java.io.Serializable, DmcNamedObjectIF
public class MvcControllerDMO
extends MvcDefinitionDMO
implements DmcNamedObjectIF, java.io.Serializable

The MvcController class allows for the definition of controllers. The abstract controller generated by this definition will automatically register for the events you specify via the handlesEvent attribute. Likewise, it will have a standard handleEvent() method that forwards typed events to abstract handler functions that you'll have to write.

Generated from the extgwt schema at version 0.1
